value.name: NBA All Star Dylan Wang
value.overview: The 4-episode Tencent Video reality mini-series follows Dylan Wang's 2024 NBA All-Star Game journey. As the Tencent NBA Experience Ambassador, Wang travels to Indiana to serve as a commentator for the event, immersing himself in the local basketball culture. He also participates in the All-Star Celebrity Game and meets his idol, LeBron James.
